data.description: Lovely spacious home on private lakefront setting in Kenwood Village! This former model home offers a large island kitchen with space to relax & entertain on oversized patio. Enjoy lake views from kitchen, family area and owners' suite. This 3bed/2bath is ready for new owners. Nicely appointed with paver driveway, sidewalk and canopied oaks. This pretty community has private pool & tennis and is close to restaurants & shopping. Low HOA!
